text: Something that I think is going overlooked in this whole situation is the role of isolation. This will be a tough time not solely on the illness and lack of entertainment but also that without routines people can fall into serious depressive episodes. Check on your friends
PLAY & Let The Fun Begin Like + RT + Click https://www.reddeergames.com Did You see it? pic.twitter.com/45a6EF3ixr

Considering this is a world pandemic. This is crazy for the whole world and it affects us all different but for me it’s taken any healing I had already done and caused me to go into a complete depressive state. Packing my room is going to be the worst time for me.
I switch between Cold Case and GBBO. I feel manic depressive lol.

i know remission is a thing but i have persistent depressive disorder which means i am constantly in a state of depression and i’m not really sure how i can ever be happy with a mood disorder like that.

As I was reading the latest things that Price Harry has said...sudentley I realied that is like I am hearing my brother who is an Pquisofrenic Border Line Manico Depressive... It is incredible the similarities... https://twitter.com/prince_scarf/status/1237571177238781953 …
that’s all of my tweets for the month before i disappear for a while and then come back in a few weeks in another depressive state to rant thanks for tuning in goodnight
